  "remarks": "CDi.016 Title: Dr. Designation: FDLR President. Reported to have died in Prison In Germany on 16 April 2019.  Arrested by German authorities on 17 November 2009 and found guilty by a German court on 28 September 2015 of leadership of a foreign terrorist group and aiding in war crimes. Received a 13-year sentence and is in prison in Germany as of June 2016. Re-elected FDLR President on 29 November 2014 for a five-year term.; Listing: Listed by 1533 Committee on: 1 Nov. 2005 (amended on 13 Oct. 2016, 25 February 2020)",
